document_data.History:
On the battle near [[Ostrav]] of [[Mirtul 2]] when [[Sergor Marsk]] stole Gareth Dragonsbane's soul for the [[Cult of the Dragon]], Drigor Bersk was fighting by the King's side.

Drigor Bersk participated in the meeting where Pavel Shemov explained [[Brimstone (drake)|Brimstone]]'s plans to Queen [[Christine Dragonsbane]] on [[Kythorn 25]]. He later joined the team sent into the [[Plane of Shadow]] to recover the King's soul on [[Kythorn 26]].{{cite book/The Rite||12}} He was also part of King Dragonsbane's offensive against the [[Vaasa]]n horde once the King was awake, on [[Flamerule 11]].{{cite book/The Rite||13}}

He was sent to the council of wyrms of the Feast of the Moon in Thentia, on behalf of King Dragonsbane, where he participated in the Grand Divination. Drigor Bersk perished on [[Nightal 6]] of {{yearlink|1373}}, decapitated by one of [[Sammaster]]'s guardian [[ironwyrm golem]]s in the ''dracorage mythal''.
